  <summary date="2020-06-04T15:08:04Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Home Loan Quality Transparency Act of 2019 

This&#160;bill expands requirements for public disclosures by depository institutions&#160;and credit unions regarding mortgages and home equity lines of credit. Specifically, institutions originating fewer than 500 mortgage loans or open-end lines of credit annually are no longer exempt from certain financial reporting.</summary>
